
<div class="row mb-3">
  <div class="col-md-12">
    <h1>
      All drinks
    </h1>
    
    <div>Below is a list of all drinks from which you can choose from: </div>

  <a><img src="https://image.shutterstock.com/image-photo/cup-coffee-latte-beans-isolated-260nw-583224151.jpg">
